00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:02.040
After they are using your app, you can't just take

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:03.840
that for granted.

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:09.110
Having a good and healthy communication with your user base is really

00:05:09.110 --> 00:05:09.840
good.

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:17.120
And communities will always be very happy to be acknowledged and be

00:05:17.270 --> 00:05:18.840
listened to.

00:05:18.840 --> 00:05:25.120
So, please, also, be very careful because since people

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:31.830
speak different languages and not the English is not their first language

00:05:31.890 --> 00:05:35.840
, words can be understood in different ways.

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:40.840
So, please be very mindful about your wording and stuff.

00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:47.820
It can be very impactful of your success of your app.

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:51.840
You can scare away many users.

