00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:23.820
It's relevant.

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:27.840
It's meaningful in the region.

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:32.050
And so, I know it's not easy to solve this

00:07:32.050 --> 00:07:34.840
problem, to have a good algorithm.

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:41.880
But you can also have, though, we have a big

00:07:42.270 --> 00:07:46.790
community of developers here and builders and stuff.

00:07:46.840 --> 00:07:49.840
You can always try to solve this problem together.

00:07:51.840 --> 00:07:58.640
Also, the creators also need to understand if it's worth

00:07:58.640 --> 00:08:00.840
to use your app.

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:07.840
